The paper proposes a deep learning approach for online unsupervised transfer learning, which involves techniques from machine learning, artificial intelligence, computer vision, and neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
